Class BolusCalculatorBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.calculator.BolusCalculatorBuilder
public class BolusCalculatorBuilder extends Object
A builder object for filling data into BolusCalculator when response messages are received from the pump.
